{
  "texts": [
    "T5-based approach has limitations in terms of model parameters compared to LLMs (large language models).",
    "These limitations persist, although there have been significant developments in this area, including prompt engineering, data augmentation, contrastive learning, multitask learning, and extensions to the T5 encoder and decoder components.",
    "With the growing amount of text data from social media and online comments, it is crucial to increase the accuracy and efficiency of ACOSQE.",
    "This section will mainly focus on these challenges and potential solutions.",
    "A significant challenge with ACOSQE is the lack of large-scale and diverse datasets covering various fields, scenarios, and languages."
  ]
}